dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.transportprotocols

Interface IFlexrayArTpConnection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, ITpConnection

    public interface IFlexrayArTpConnection
extends IEntity, ITpConnection
    IFlexrayArTpConnection: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    A connection within a channel identifies the sender and the receiver of this particular communication. The FlexRay Autosar Tp module routes a Pdu through this connection.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!

      • getReversedTpSdu

        IIPdu getReversedTpSdu()
        Query the undirectional to-one association ReversedTpSdu.

        Reference to the IPdu that is segmented by the Transport Protocol. If support of both sending and receiving is used, this association references the IPdu used for the additional second direction. The source address of the transmitted NPdu is determined by the configured target CommunicationConnector. The target address of the transmitted NPdu is determined by the configured source CommunicationConnector.

        Returns:
        the referenced entity or null
        Throws:
        TresosDBException - in case of an error
